PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FAdditional lessons in schools will
OL,7,Faccompany the ban on how to use media
OL,8,Fand deal with artificial intelligence.
OL,10,FSpain's prime minister said in
OL,11,FFebruary that his government plans to
OL,12,Fban social media for people under 16.
OL,14,FPedro Sanchez said the move is
OL,15,Fdesigned to shield young people from
OL,16,Fthe harms of online content.
OL,26,@vD@Hrp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/25
