PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,F"Today, our children are exposed to a
OL,7,Fspace they were never meant to
OL,8,Fnavigate alone," Sanchez said. "We
OL,9,Fwill no longer accept that," he said
OL,10,Fat a summit in the United Arab
OL,11,FEmirates.
OL,13,FSanchez said Spain has joined five
OL,14,Fother European countries - known as
OL,15,Fthe "Coalition of the Digitally
OL,16,FWilling" - to coordinate and enforce
OL,17,Fcross-border regulation of the new
OL,18,Frules.
OL,20,FThe coalition will hold its first
OL,21,Fmeeting in the coming days, he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@SrppD@`OUxD@HO]
