OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FIn January, French lawmakers approved
OL,7,Fa bill banning social media for
OL,8,Fchildren under 15.
OL,10,FThe bill passed through the divided
OL,11,FFrench National Assembly by 130 votes
OL,12,Fto 121 and will be discussed by the
OL,13,FFrench Senate in the coming weeks.
OL,15,FFrench President Emmanuel Macron has
OL,16,Fasked for the legislation to be fast-
OL,17,Ftracked, so that it could be in place
OL,18,Fby the start of the next school year
OL,19,Fin September.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
