CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,F"Banning social media for those under
OL,7,F15: this is what scientists recommend,
OL,8,Fand this is what the French people are
OL,9,Foverwhelmingly calling for," he said
OL,10,Fafter the vote.
OL,12,F"Because our children's brains are not
OL,13,Ffor sale ` neither to American
OL,14,Fplatforms nor to Chinese networks.
OL,15,FBecause their dreams must not be
OL,16,Fdictated by algorithms."
OL,18,FIt would also ban the use of mobile
OL,19,Fphones in high schools.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@\O]tD@AOUxD@XO]
