OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FDenmark announced in October that it
OL,7,Fwould be moving towards banning social
OL,8,Fmedia for users under 15.
OL,10,FPrime Minister Mette Frederiksen said
OL,11,Fat the time that social platforms were
OL,12,F"stealing our children's childhood".
OL,14,FSpeaking at the opening of the Danish
OL,15,Fparliament, Frederiksen said her
OL,16,Fgovernment would propose a ban that
OL,17,Falso gives parents the option to
OL,18,Fapprove social media use from age 13.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/25
