FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,F"We have said yes to mobile phones in
OL,7,Four children's lives in the best
OL,8,Fsense. So they can call home and
OL,9,Fcommunicate with their friends," she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"But the reality is that we have let a
OL,13,Fmonster loose. Never before have so
OL,14,Fmany children and young people
OL,15,Fsuffered from anxiety and depression,"
OL,16,FFrederiksen added.
