OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FCanada has introduced legislation that
OL,7,Fcould bar children younger than 16
OL,8,Ffrom having social media accounts
OL,9,Funless the companies show they can
OL,10,Fmake their platforms safe.
OL,12,F"We are failing our children. Enough
OL,13,Fis enough," Marc Miller, Canada's
OL,14,Fculture minister, said. "We need basic
OL,15,Fprotection in place."
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@KO]vD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
