OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FThe legislation covers seven types of
OL,7,Fharmful content including content that
OL,8,Finduces children to harm themselves,
OL,9,Fcontent that incites violence and
OL,10,Ffoments hatred and non-consensual
OL,11,Fintimate images.
OL,13,FA new regulator, the Digital Safety
OL,14,FCommission of Canada, will be created
OL,15,Fas part of the plans. Miller said
OL,16,Fplatforms will need to prove they are
OL,17,Fsafe and age verification measures
OL,18,Fwill also be introduced.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
