CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FNorway's Prime Minister Jonas Gahr
OL,7,FStore has also proposed a ban for
OL,8,Fusers under 15 years of age and his
OL,9,Fgovernment launched a public
OL,10,Fconsultation for a new law in June.
OL,12,F"This is one of the most pressing
OL,13,Fsocial and cultural challenges of our
OL,14,Ftime, and it cannot be solved through
OL,15,Fnational measures alone. We aim to
OL,16,Fstrengthen European cooperation to
OL,17,Fensure a safe digital environment for
OL,18,Fchildren and young people," Store said
OL,19,Flast year.
OL,26,@oD@Co|tD@AOUzD@[O]zD@_o|
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/25
