CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FAlongside the ban, Norway has said it
OL,7,Fwould issue national recommendations
OL,8,Fon screen times and remove mobile
OL,9,Fphones from schools through national
OL,10,Frecommendations.
OL,12,FUK ministers have launched a
OL,13,Fconsultation on whether to ban under-
OL,14,F16s from social media platforms, while
OL,15,Fsome ministers also want a legal ban
OL,16,Fon phones in schools.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
