OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FOvernight curfews, breaks to prevent
OL,7,F"doom-scrolling", and introducing an
OL,8,FAustralian-style social media ban
OL,9,Fwhich would raise the digital age of
OL,10,Fconsent, are some of the proposals the
OL,11,Fgovernment is considering.
OL,13,FLabour MPs have called for "urgent
OL,14,Faction" from Starmer to raise the
OL,15,Fminimum age for access to social media
OL,16,Fplatforms. ITV News understands at
OL,17,Fleast 66 Labour MPs want the
OL,18,Fgovernment to bring in a social media
OL,19,Fban for under-16s.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@PO]
