CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FWhile the government is so far yet to
OL,7,Fintroduce a ban, in June, Starmer
OL,8,Fannounced that big tech companies
OL,9,Fincluding Google and Apple must
OL,10,Fintroduce controls to "prevent
OL,11,Fchildren from sending and receiving
OL,12,Fsexually explicit images" ` giving
OL,13,Fthem three months to comply with the
OL,14,Flaw.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/25
