OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News former
OL,7,FSafeguarding Minister Jess Phillips,
OL,8,Fwho quit cabinet in May over a lack of
OL,9,Fprogress by the government on social
OL,10,Fmedia protections, said the "the
OL,11,Fwriting is on the wall" for a social
OL,12,Fmedia ban for minors.
OL,14,FA new law to protect children from
OL,15,Faddictive and harmful content online
OL,16,Fcame into effect in Brazil in March.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
