FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FChildren under 16 are now required to
OL,7,Flink their social media accounts to a
OL,8,Flegal guardian to ensure supervision.
OL,9,FThe legislation also prohibits
OL,10,Fplatforms from using addictive
OL,11,Ffeatures such as infinite scroll and
OL,12,Fthe automatic play of videos.
OL,14,FDigital services also must implement
OL,15,Fan effective age verification
OL,16,Fmechanism that goes beyond self-
OL,17,Fdeclaration that the user is over 18
OL,18,Fto protect them from accessing
OL,19,Finappropriate or prohibited material.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/25
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
