CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1781215878
OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,F"The government has instructed all
OL,7,Fdigital platforms operating in
OL,8,FIndonesia to immediately bring their
OL,9,Fproducts, features and services into
OL,10,Fcompliance with applicable
OL,11,Fregulations," said Indonesia's
OL,12,FCommunication and Digital Affairs
OL,13,FMinister Meutya Hafid.
OL,15,F"There will be no compromise on
OL,16,Fcompliance, and every business entity
OL,17,Foperating in Indonesia is required to
OL,18,Fcomply with Indonesian law."
OL,20,FHow have social media companies
OL,21,Fresponded?
