OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FMeta, the parent company of Instagram,
OL,7,FFacebook, and Threads, started rolling
OL,8,Fout its plan to ban young people from
OL,9,Fits platforms in the run-up to
OL,10,FAustralia's ban.
OL,12,FUsers aged 13 to 15 were notified that
OL,13,Ftheir access to those sites would be
OL,14,Flimited from December 4, with all
OL,15,Fusers impacted by the law to be
OL,16,Fremoved before it took effect on
OL,17,FDecember 10.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G22/25
