OL,3,CWhat countries are planning to ban
OL,4,Csocial media for under-16s?
OL,6,FX, meanwhile, said it had "serious
OL,7,Fconcerns" around the "lawfulness" of
OL,8,Fthe minimum age for social media.
OL,10,F"We are especially concerned about the
OL,11,Fpotential negative impact that the
OL,12,FSocial Media Minimum Age will have on
OL,13,Fthe human rights of children and young
OL,14,Fpeople," it said in September.
OL,16,FYouTube described Australia's ban as
OL,17,F"disappointing" and said the law "will
OL,18,Fnot fulfill its promise to make kids
OL,19,Fsafer online". It said the law would
OL,20,Fin fact "make Australian kids less
OL,21,Fsafe on YouTube".
